{"tid":2421594,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"燦烈神隱4個月首發聲！　道歉粉絲：會努力證明大家的信任沒錯付","createTime":"2021-02-24T15:09:00.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-25T02:36:41.000Z","uid":74065,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"1bcdbbb255b9f3515b68da029778da007d234deb","tid":2421594,"uid":74065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-24T15:09:00.000Z","msg":"南韓男團EXO成員燦烈2020年10月被自稱前女友的網友爆料暗中「劈腿10多人」，衝擊爆料點燃網友與粉絲戰火，然而經紀公司SM娛樂隨後回應「沒有要發表正式的聲明」，模糊立場再度引發熱議。而他本人在惹議後，神隱至今已經4個月，終於在24日晚間寫下長文，向粉絲致歉。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/5470/d5470618.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F5470%2Fd5470618.jpg&h=828ecf48&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲燦烈沉默4個月首度發聲。（圖／翻攝燦烈IG）<br />\n[廣告]請繼續往下閱讀...<br />\n<br />\n燦烈24日在SM娛樂創建的官方粉絲團Lysn上發布道歉文，寫下這段時間以來的心情，開頭便向粉絲道歉，表示事情爆發後經過了無數次的思考，到底要如何表達心意。接著提到在前陣子生日時，收到粉絲送的應援以及信件。<br />\n<br />\n燦烈表示粉絲的信他都一一讀過，說道：「抱歉和感激的心越來越強烈，無數次苦惱著該怎麼守護、報答EXO-L（EXO粉絲名）們珍貴的心意，反覆思索如何才能不讓大家擔心。」並強調會努力證明粉絲的信任沒有錯付。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/5470/d5470617.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F5470%2Fd5470617.jpg&h=5baedde4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲燦烈向粉絲道歉。（圖／翻攝燦烈IG）<br />\n<br />\n最後，燦烈也強調出道進入第9年，自己絕對不會忘記9年前出道時的初衷，承諾：「我絕對不會忘記，我會好好守護大家給予的愛，EXO-L們要一直健康，謝謝你們。」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n觀眾要求「刪光燦烈片段」！ 粉絲灌爆《叢林》官網：別傷害他<br />\n<br />\n快訊／燦烈被爆「多劈」粉敲碗公司法務部！SM沉默半日終於回應<br />\n<br />\n燦烈曾說到死之前才戀愛 前女友打臉：吃遍女偶像、直播主、YouTuber和空姐"},{"pid":"f889965058632a55a7b2734031ebdb3e5ee468f0","tid":2421594,"uid":143093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-24T15:10:04.000Z","msg":"偷食啫"},{"pid":"2853d2869c84cdc7e39c011f902379cbab69d9da","tid":2421594,"uid":294121,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-24T15:11:32.000Z","msg":"要自己打飛機打足四個月<br />\n出返黎一定日日食女食到癲"},{"pid":"d0a2c104dde6ed9bcd944f670cb1e03fa25d7a2c","tid":2421594,"uid":274500,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-24T15:13:43.000Z","msg":"咁姐係個爆料係真係假<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0c32be310676ba943add76ee7551a9b507b510fa","tid":2421594,"uid":165368,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-24T15:15:02.000Z","msg":"@牙邊<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/28.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3ad38f63b003395a3eef46a690041d90b165303d","tid":2421594,"uid":93096,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-24T15:16:30.000Z","msg":"傻仔邊...<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/28.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"896cffce999b0fb328c7d976e9157b435a09846f","tid":2421594,"uid":211461,"like":23,"dislike":0,"score":23,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-24T15:20:18.000Z","msg":"睇錯燦神 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://resource01-proxy.ulifestyle.com.hk/res/v3/image/content/2470000/2473934/3881901512_1db10ca5ce_600.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fresource01-proxy.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2470000%2F2473934%2F3881901512_1db10ca5ce_600.jpg&h=ccb0dde1&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"5f6018cacab7fda4ec5a047e35e0192859ef634c","tid":2421594,"uid":95,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"896cffce999b0fb328c7d976e9157b435a09846f","tid":2421594,"uid":211461,"like":23,"dislike":0,"score":23,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-24T15:20:18.000Z","msg":"睇錯燦神 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://resource01-proxy.ulifestyle.com.hk/res/v3/image/content/2470000/2473934/3881901512_1db10ca5ce_600.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fresource01-proxy.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2470000%2F2473934%2F3881901512_1db10ca5ce_600.jpg&h=ccb0dde1&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-24T15:51:43.000Z","msg":"屌 same<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9eb83a07fe1a622fcb2a8a